This program depends on the following third party modules ZODB and zodbpickle, install them with these commands:

    pip3 install ZODB
    pip3 install zodbpickle

You shall setup a development environment prior running this command, because it may require a C compiler.

For audio playback, you need the mplayer command, the program 'cmplayer' in tool directory is for better control of the mplayer.
